BMO Capital Markets Hires Santa-Maria, Brichkowski for U.S. Unit

-- B y   D o u g   A l e x a n d e r
-- 
2011-09-12T12:44:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-12/bmo-capital-markets-hires-santa-maria-brichkowski-for-u-s-unit.html
BMO Capital Markets hired Robert Brichkowski and Steve Santa-Maria to expand its foreign-exchange
business in  New York .  The investment-banking unit of  Bank of Montreal (BMO)  hired
Santa-Maria as a managing director responsible for expanding the
firm’s institutional business, the Toronto-based company said in
an e-mailed statement today. Brichkowski joins as a managing
director and is responsible for expanding the firm’s U.S. Real
Money FX Sales business. Both are based in New York.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Doug Alexander in Toronto at 
